messages.TRMSG_PRE_BATTLE:
I’m proud of my Pokémon!
Here, I’ll show you why!
messages.TRMSG_DEFEAT:
Youch! You sure showed me how tough
you were.
messages.TRMSG_POST_BATTLE:
Oh, what have we here?
That’s a Pokédex!It records Pokémon data upon
sight? I’ve never seen one before!I heard you can move the sun or
moon icon to check the Pokémon habitat map by time of day!
messages.TRMSG_REMATCH:
I take down details in my notebook
about Pokémon I’ve battled.I’ll write more data down about your
Pokémon!
